          "text": "Yetis gain a +4 status bonus to saves against fear and against spells and abilities that affect dreams. A yeti who falls prey to a supernatural nightmare loses this ability and becomes permanently enraged, gaining a +1 status bonus to attack and damage rolls and a \u20131 status penalty to AC.",
